The mother of emir of Kano, Alh. Aminu Ado Bayero, Hajiya Maryam Ado Bayero is dead. The late Hajiya Maryam is also the mother of another first class chief, the emir of Bichi, Alh. Nasiru Ado Bayero. Hajiya Maryam passed on early Saturday in Cairo, Egypt after a protracted illness, a palace source confirmed. The late Maryam was a princess and elder sister to the present emir of Ilorin Alh.Ibrahim Sulu Gambari. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .